Information(Title: "Curd Rice", ImageName: "curd rice", dish: "To make curd rice, mix cooked rice with plain yogurt, green chilies, ginger, and salt. In a pan, temper mustard seeds, cumin seeds, dried red chilies, and curry leaves in hot oil. Pour over rice-yogurt mixture, mix, and serve chilled or at room temperature."),
Information(Title: "Coriander Rice", ImageName: "coriander", dish: "To make coriander rice, blend fresh coriander leaves, green chilies, ginger, and garlic into a paste. Sauté the paste in oil until fragrant, then mix with cooked rice and salt. Garnish with chopped coriander leaves before serving hot."),
