Information(Title: "Tomato Rice", ImageName: "tomato", dish: "To make tomato rice, sauté onions and garlic in oil until golden brown. Add chopped tomatoes and cook until soft. Stir in cooked rice, along with turmeric, chili powder, and salt to taste. Mix well, garnish with cilantro, and serve hot."),
Information(Title: "Idli", ImageName: "idli", dish: "To prepare idli, first soak rice and urad dal (split black gram) separately for a few hours. Grind them into a smooth batter and let it ferment overnight. Pour the batter into idli molds and steam until cooked through. Serve hot with chutney and sambar."),
